Package com.cafean.client.analysis

Class EmbeddedConnectionMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.analysis.EmbeddedConnectionMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    public class EmbeddedConnectionMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.undo.StateEditable
    This data structure is a map of the embedded connections in any drawn-sub component inside a ViewComponent. This map allows quickly searching for embedded connections.
